{
  "epId": 2966,
  "name": "千夜浮梦",
  "desc": "<p>浮映千夜之梦的灯盏，苍翠的光中流溢着遥世的歌。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/02/36540823/afd146c520b3a0bd72489a3426d8f283_6485794778533054261.png",
